abstract ={The influence of heaven and its contents on Iranian poets and artists hasproduced beautiful descriptions of heaven, the sun, the moon, the stars and other constellations in Persian poems which illustrate the power of the Iranian poets in creatingbeautiful images,exotic art and elegance. The present article is an attempt to show the waycertain astronomical imagesare used in Anvari&#8217;spoetry and also the poet&#8217;s innovation in languageand diction is studied. Moreover,by showing the art of Anvari&#8217;s verbal painting and conceptual creativity, the researchersendeavor to explain some of his complicated verses.},  
